refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public boolDirectoryIterator::isWritable
Determines if the current DirectoryIterator item is writable.

  &reftitle.examples;



    DirectoryIterator::isWritable example


      This example lists the files and directories which can be 
      opened for writing in the directory containing the script.



<?php
$iterator = new DirectoryIterator(dirname(__FILE__));
foreach ($iterator as $fileinfo) {
    if ($fileinfo->isWritable()) {
        echo $fileinfo->getFilename() . "\n";
    }
}
?>


